```

This Spoon processor:
1. Identifies all `javax.jws` imports in the codebase
2. Replaces them with their `jakarta.jws` equivalents
3. Preserves all import properties (static, on-demand)
4. Also handles `javax.xml.ws` imports which are also part of the Jakarta EE migration
